benchmark_config.jira_title: Implement/Test API: PUT /1.0/kb/accounts/{accountId}/paymentMethods/{paymentMethodId}/setDefault - Set the default payment method

covered: Valid Request: Scenarios cover successful setting of default payment methods with various parameters.
Invalid Data: Scenarios test for invalid accountId and paymentMethodId formats.
Non-Existing Resource: Scenarios handle cases where the accountId or paymentMethodId does not exist.
Authorization: Scenarios check for unauthorized access and missing required headers.
gaps: Concurrency Issues: No tests cover race conditions when multiple users try to set the default payment method simultaneously.
Performance: No tests assess the performance under load or with a large number of unpaid invoices.
Edge Cases: Scenarios for extreme cases, such as very large pluginProperty arrays or partial UUIDs, are limited.
recommendations: Add tests for concurrency issues to ensure the system handles simultaneous requests correctly.
Include performance tests to evaluate the API under load.
Expand edge case scenarios to cover more extreme input variations.
